<span class=title> Re: Spell Research</span><hr size=1> This was posted on my guilds private section:<br>
<br>
Copy/paste from the EQTrader board. Notice how each priest class is researchable by only one arcane class. As always, they may wind up changing recipes or something else before this goes live. Just thought I'd give you a heads up on what is known.<br>
<br>
New research book: 8 slot book, no drop, and you can't get it unless you have the right research skill(101). <br>
<br>
PRIEST CLASS RECIPES <br>
<br>
Note Druids use Wizards to do the reserch for them, Clerics use Necromancers, and Shamans use Magicians. <br>
<br>
Shaman - researched by magicians <br>
====== <br>
